We note that replication results for a few markers are not always available for genome-scan data. Moreover, replication of an entire GWAS on the same platform gives rise to new combined results (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
\usepackage{amsfonts} 
